TEXTUAL_CONTENT.content: Setalarmforme.com provides simplest way to set alarms for X minutes from now.
Alarms setup by Setalarmforme.com are accurate. You can rely on us completely to start alarm after $variable minutes.
You can setup alarm for $variable minutes from now on any operating system, like Windows/Mac/Linux/Android/iPhone.
Setalarmforme.com does not require users to login for setting alarm for $variable minutes from now. No user information is send to our servers.
Using Setalarmforme.com you can set alarm to start after $variable minutes from current time, in any time zone.

TEXTUAL_CONTENT.header: No need to install any software
TEXTUAL_CONTENT.content: Setalarmforme.com is a cloud and web based application. You do not need to install any software to use Setalarmforme.com while setting alarms for $variable minutes from now.

HOW_TO_CONTENT.heading: How to set alarm for $variable minutes:
steps: Click submit to set alarm, that's it !.

FAQ.question: How many seconds from now, will the alarm ring ?
FAQ.answer: When you setup alarm for $variable minutes from now, the alarm will ring after { % $variable * 60 % } seconds.

FAQ.question: Can I rely on Setalarmforme.com  to setup alarm for $variable minutes from now ?
FAQ.answer: If you have set alarm for $variable minutes from now, you can be 100% sure that alarm will ring after $variable minutes. You can trust us completely.

FAQ.question: What will happen to the alarm that I have set, if I refresh the browser ?
FAQ.answer: The alarm will still ring after $variable minutes, even if you refresh the browser, since we store the information in browser's local cache.

FAQ.question: What will happen to the alarm that I have set, if I close the tab of browser in which Setalarmforme.com is opened ?
FAQ.answer: It will be gone. The alarm will not ring after $variable minutes, if you close the tab.

FAQ.question: What will happen to the alarm that I have set, if I close the browser ?
FAQ.answer: It will be gone. The alarm will not ring after $variable minutes, if you close the browser.
